txt.en: Gámnakur and his pack can be found in the Mokál Rukh.\n\nYou should defeat Gámnakur and his pack.

A bounty notice is pinned to the board, stamped with the royal seal of Gondor:

'Wanted: Gámnakur and his pack
Deep in the Mokál Rukh lurks the dire-wolf Gámnakur. The Conquest of Mordor requests an adventurer to remove him and his pack.'
Deep in the Mokál Rukh lurks a dire-wolf named Gámnakur. The Conquest of Mordor requests an adventurer to go and defeat him.
